@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5" style="min-height: 100vh;">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center mb-5">At PC3, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our services.</p>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>We collect information directly from you, such as your name, email address, and any other information you provide to us. We also collect information about your interactions with our website and services, including IP address, browser type, and usage data.</p>

            <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
                <li>To communicate with you about updates, offers, and promotions</li>
                <li>To protect against, investigate, and deter fraudulent, unauthorized, or illegal activity</li>
                <li>To comply with legal obligations and enforce our policies</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Sharing Your Information</h3>
            <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide our services, comply with the law, or protect our rights. We may share non-personal, aggregated information with our partners for analytics and marketing purposes.</p>

            <h3>Your Choices and Rights</h3>
            <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. You can also opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in those communications or contacting us directly.</p>

            <h3>Data Security</h3>
            <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.</p>

            <h3>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on our website and updating the effective date. Your continued use of our services after any changes indicates your acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@pc3.com">privacy@pc3.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Custom Styles -->
<style>
    .container {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #00796b;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #004d40;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    p, ul {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #333333;
    }
    ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    a {
        color: #00796b;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>
